name: COHMAP chron 1
notes: 24 cm core from a sedge meadow in low arctic tundra. One C-14 date. Date at surface a guess by TW. No evidence of cultural disturbance at the top of the core. Age bounds for application of the model: top = 0; bottom = 1020.
